| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-7621 — Recovery Inhibition (devman)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 3e7c2325-8c7f-5034-bc6f-48910ec60a5a"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
